<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>USSH - Phúc Lộc Thọ | Trang chủ</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/canvas-confetti@1.6.0/dist/confetti.browser.min.js"></script>

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-red: #D32F2F; 
            --soft-red: #FFEBEE;
            --accent-red: #EF5350;
            --text-dark: #2D3436;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            --transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
            --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { color: var(--text-dark); background-color: #fff; line-height: 1.6; }

        /* --- Header --- */
        header {
            position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%;
            padding: 15px 8%;
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            background: var(--glass);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1);
        }

        .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; text-decoration: none; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
        .logo img { height: 50px; }
        .logo-text { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--primary-red); letter-spacing: -0.5px; }

        /* --- CỤM 3 LOGO Ở GIỮA --- */
        .header-center {
            display: flex; gap: 20px; position: absolute; left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%); z-index: 1;
        }
        .header-center a {
            display: block; width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%;
            overflow: hidden; border: 2px solid transparent;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transition: var(--transition); background: white;
        }
        .header-center a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.15) translateY(-2px); border-color: var(--primary-red);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(211,47,47,0.3);
        }
        .header-center img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

        nav { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
        nav ul { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 30px; }
        nav a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--text-dark); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: var(--transition); }
        nav a:hover { color: var(--primary-red); }

        /* --- Hero Section --- */
        .hero {
            height: 100vh; width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            text-align: center; color: white; position: relative; overflow: hidden; 
        }

        .hero-content { max-width: 900px; padding: 0 20px; animation: fadeInUp 1s ease; z-index: 1; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 35px; line-height: 1.2; text-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
        
        .btn-cta {
            background: var(--primary-red); color: white; padding: 16px 45px;
            border-radius: 50px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800;
            display: inline-block; transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.4); background: var(--accent-red); }

        /* --- Sections --- */
        section { padding: 100px 10%; }
        .section-title { text-align: center; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--primary-red); margin-bottom: 60px; font-weight: 800; }
        
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; }
        .card { 
            background: white; padding: 45px; border-radius: 25px; 
            border: 1px solid var(--soft-red); transition: var(--transition); 
            text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); border-color: var(--accent-red); box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
        .card .icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 20px; display: block; }
        .card h3 { color: var(--primary-red); margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.6rem; }

        /* --- CSS Container dùng chung --- */
        .info-container { background: var(--soft-red); padding: 50px; border-radius: 35px; margin-bottom: 50px; }
        .placeholder-box { background: #eee; border: 2px dashed #ccc; color: #999; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 600; }

        /* --- Form CSS --- */
        .form-input {
            padding: 10px 15px; border: 1.5px solid white; border-radius: 12px; 
            outline: none; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: 0.3s;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; background: white; resize: vertical; width: 100%;
        }
        .form-input:focus { border-color: var(--primary-red); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(211,47,47,0.1); }
        .btn-submit {
            background: var(--primary-red); color: white; padding: 14px; width: 100%;
            border: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.05rem;
            cursor: pointer; transition: var(--transition); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(211,47,47,0.3);
        }
        .btn-submit:hover { background: var(--accent-red); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(211,47,47,0.4); }
        
        .success-popup {
            display: none; background: #d4edda; color: #155724; padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 10px; text-align: center; font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb; animation: slideIn 0.3s ease; font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* --- Profile Card CSS --- */
        .profile-card {
            background: var(--soft-red); border-radius: 25px; padding: 25px;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; border: 1px solid rgba(211,47,47,0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .profile-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(211,47,47,0.15); }
        .profile-card-inner { display: flex; gap: 20px; width: 100%; }
        
        .profile-card-img {
            width: 100px; height: 130px; background: white; border-radius: 15px;
            flex-shrink: 0; overflow: hidden; border: 4px solid white; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .profile-card-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
        .profile-card-info { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .profile-card-info h3 { color: var(--primary-red); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 3px; }
        .profile-card-info p { margin: 0; color: #444; }
        .profile-card-info strong { color: var(--text-dark); }

        .profile-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; width: 100%; border-top: 1px dashed rgba(211,47,47,0.2); padding-top: 15px; }
        .btn-reject { flex: 1; padding: 12px; background: #fff; color: #666; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn-reject:hover { background: #e0e0e0; }
        .btn-accept { flex: 1; padding: 12px; background: var(--primary-red); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(211,47,47,0.3); }
        .btn-accept:hover { background: var(--accent-red); transform: translateY(-2px); }

        /* --- Toast Popup Chung --- */
        #global-toast {
            display: none; position: fixed; top: 100px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #d4edda; color: #155724; padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); z-index: 9999; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
        }

        /* --- Contact & Maps --- */
        .contact-container { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 50px; background: var(--soft-red); padding: 50px; border-radius: 35px; }
        .contact-info h2 { color: var(--primary-red); margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 2rem; }
        .member-list { list-style: none; margin: 25px 0; }
        .member-list li { padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; }
        .map-box { border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; border: 8px solid white; box-shadow: var(--shadow); height: 400px; }

        /* =========================================
           CHATBOT & GPA CSS
           ========================================= */
        #chat-trigger, #gpa-trigger {
            position: fixed; bottom: 30px; width: 65px; height: 65px; background: var(--primary-red);
            border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.4); z-index: 1001; transition: var(--transition);
        }
        #chat-trigger { right: 30px; } #gpa-trigger { left: 30px; }
        #chat-trigger:hover { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg); } #gpa-trigger:hover { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-5deg); }

        .widget-window {
            position: fixed; bottom: 105px; width: 360px; background: white;
            border-radius: 25px; box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); display: none;
            flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; z-index: 1001; animation: slideIn 0.4s ease;
        }
        #chat-window { right: 30px; height: 520px; }
        #gpa-window { left: 30px; max-height: 550px; }

        .widget-header { color: white; padding: 20px; font-weight: 700; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .chat-header { background: var(--primary-red); } .gpa-header { background: #2D3436; }
        
        .chat-body { flex: 1; padding: 20px; overflow-y: auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; background: #fdfdfd; }
        .msg { padding: 12px 18px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.95rem; max-width: 85%; line-height: 1.4; }
        .msg.bot { background: var(--soft-red); align-self: flex-start; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; color: var(--primary-red); }
        .msg.user { background: var(--primary-red); color: white; align-self: flex-end; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; }
        .chat-input { padding: 15px; display: flex; gap: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; background: white; }
        .chat-input input { flex: 1; border: 1.5px solid #eee; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 30px; outline: none; transition: 0.3s; }
        .chat-input input:focus { border: 1.5px solid var(--primary-red); }

        .gpa-tabs { display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; background: #fafafa;}
        .tab-btn { flex: 1; padding: 15px; border: none; background: none; font-weight: 800; color: #999; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; font-size: 0.9rem;}
        .tab-btn.active { color: var(--primary-red); border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary-red); background: white;}
        .gpa-body { padding: 20px; overflow-y: auto; background: #fdfdfd; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; max-height: 350px; }
        .subject-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; animation: fadeInUp 0.3s ease; }
        .subject-row input { width: 80px; padding: 10px; border: 1.5px solid #eee; border-radius: 10px; outline: none; text-align: center; font-weight: 600;}
        .subject-row select { flex: 1; padding: 10px; border: 1.5px solid #eee; border-radius: 10px; outline: none; font-weight: 600;}
        .subject-row .btn-remove { background: var(--soft-red); color: var(--primary-red); border: none; width: 35px; height: 35px; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; transition: 0.2s;}
        .subject-row .btn-remove:hover { background: var(--primary-red); color: white; }
        .target-input-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .target-input-group label { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: #555; }
        .target-input-group input { padding: 12px; border: 1.5px solid #eee; border-radius: 10px; outline: none; font-weight: 600; width: 100%;}
        .target-input-group input:focus { border: 1.5px solid var(--primary-red); }
        .gpa-actions { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; padding: 0 20px 20px 20px; background: #fdfdfd; border-top: 1px solid transparent;}
        .btn-add-subject { background: #f0f0f0; color: #333; border: none; padding: 12px; border-radius: 15px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; transition: 0.2s; }
        .btn-add-subject:hover { background: #e0e0e0; }
        .btn-calc-gpa { background: var(--primary-red); color: white; border: none; padding: 15px; border-radius: 15px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; transition: 0.2s; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(211,47,47,0.3); width: 100%;}
        .btn-calc-gpa:hover { background: var(--accent-red); transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .gpa-result-box { text-align: center; padding: 15px; background: var(--soft-red); border-radius: 15px; border: 2px dashed var(--primary-red); margin-bottom: 10px; display: none; }
        .gpa-result-box span { display: block; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary-red); }

        /* =========================================
           CSS THÊM CHO PHẦN HỌC BỔNG (LỘC)
           ========================================= */
        .scholar-app { background: white; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow); border: 1px solid rgba(211,47,47,0.1); }
        .scholar-search { background: var(--soft-red); padding: 35px 30px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(211,47,47,0.1); }
        .scholar-search h3 { font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 25px; font-weight: 800; }
        .scholar-filters { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-end; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .s-filter-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-align: left; position: relative; }
        .s-filter-item label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 700; }
        .s-select { padding: 12px 18px; border: 1.5px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 12px; background: white; min-width: 200px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-dark); cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; }
        .s-select:hover { border-color: var(--primary-red); }
        .s-dropdown { display: none; position: absolute; top: 75px; left: 0; width: 100%; background: white; border: 1.5px solid var(--primary-red); border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(211,47,47,0.15); z-index: 10; overflow: hidden; list-style: none; }
        .s-dropdown.active { display: block; animation: fadeInUp 0.2s ease; }
        .s-dropdown li { padding: 12px 18px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f5f5; }
        .s-dropdown li:hover { background: var(--soft-red); color: var(--primary-red); }
        .s-status-btns { display: flex; gap: 10px; height: 46px; }
        .s-btn-status { padding: 0 20px; border: 1.5px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 25px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; background: white; color: #666; transition: 0.3s; }
        .s-btn-status.active { background: var(--primary-red); color: white; border-color: var(--primary-red); box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(211,47,47,0.2); }
        .scholar-content { padding: 30px 40px; }
        .s-category-wrapper { margin-bottom: 40px; scroll-margin-top: 100px; }
        .s-category-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--soft-red); padding-bottom: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .s-category-icon { width: 45px; height: 45px; background: var(--soft-red); color: var(--primary-red); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.5rem; }
        .s-category-title { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary-red); text-transform: uppercase; }
        .s-cards-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 25px; }
        .scholar-card { border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 15px; padding: 25px; background: white; display: flex; flex-direction: column; position: relative; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); transition: var(--transition); text-align: left;}
        .scholar-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(211,47,47,0.1); border-color: rgba(211,47,47,0.3); }
        .s-badge { position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 20px; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .s-badge.green { background: #d4edda; color: #155724; border: 1px solid #c3e6cb; }
        .s-badge.yellow { background: #fff3cd; color: #856404; border: 1px solid #ffeeba; }
        .s-badge.gray { background: #e2e3e5; color: #383d41; border: 1px solid #d6d8db; }
        .scholar-card h4 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--text-dark); line-height: 1.4; min-height: 50px; font-weight: 800; padding-right: 70px; }
        .s-card-details { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 25px; flex-grow: 1; padding: 0; }
        .s-card-details li { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-weight: 500; }
        .s-card-details li i { color: var(--primary-red); opacity: 0.7; margin-top: 4px; min-width: 16px; text-align: center; }
        .s-card-details li strong { color: var(--text-dark); }
        .btn-s-view { width: 100%; background-color: var(--soft-red); color: var(--primary-red); border: none; padding: 14px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 800; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 8px; text-decoration: none; }
        .btn-s-view:hover { background-color: var(--primary-red); color: white; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(211,47,47,0.2); }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeInUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
        @keyframes slideIn { from { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; } to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; } }

        @media (max-width: 992px) { .header-center { display: none; } }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
            .contact-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            nav { display: none; }
            .profile-card-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center; }
            .profile-card-img { width: 120px; height: 150px; margin-bottom: 5px;}
            .section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
            .scholar-filters { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
            .s-select { width: 100%; }
            .s-status-btns { justify-content: center; }
            .scholar-content { padding: 20px; }
            .scholar-card h4 { padding-right: 0; margin-top: 30px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="global-toast">
        🎉 Chờ chúng mình mang 'Phúc' đến nha!
    </div>

    <header>
        <a href="#" class="logo">
            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTNLG2poUhW72ORKbqy3xmyk7q3Q4HAtfcVpw&s" alt="Logo USSH">
            <span class="logo-text">USSH - PHÚC LỘC THỌ</span>
        </a>
        <div class="header-center">
            <a href="#phuc" title="Chuyển đến Phúc"><img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1Cv-g5oE3VfmFxXg6KgN5uykJDU2Lzfbt&sz=w150" alt="Logo Phúc"></a>
            <a href="#loc" title="Chuyển đến Lộc"><img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1lIzml0jGhHDmLAZJ0TG8RviZ9uaX59qV&sz=w150" alt="Logo Lộc"></a>
            <a href="#tho" title="Chuyển đến Thọ"><img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1gq8zKmGK0nZIShuBVcVn_Qp6EYm3LCxH&sz=w150" alt="Logo Thọ"></a>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#trang-chu">Trang chủ</a></li>
                <li><a href="#phuc">Phúc</a></li>
                <li><a href="#loc">Lộc</a></li>
                <li><a href="#tho">Thọ</a></li>
                <li><a href="#lien-he">Liên hệ</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="trang-chu" class="hero">
        <img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1jw4tcetWYg2pnfOYUxlpvWwYNT4H3tFe&sz=w1920"   
             alt="Background"
             style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; z-index: 0; filter: brightness(0.6);">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Phúc Lộc Thọ – Điểm tựa số cho<br>sinh viên Nhân Văn</h1>
            <a href="#huong-dan" class="btn-cta">TÌM HIỂU THÊM</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="huong-dan">
        <div class="info-container">
            <h2 style="color: var(--primary-red); margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; text-align: center;">Bí kíp trải chiếu</h2>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--text-dark);">
                <p>[Chỗ này sinh viên sẽ dẫn nội dung Bí kíp trải chiếu. Tớ đang để khung sẵn ở đây theo yêu cầu.]</p>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="placeholder-box" style="height: 400px; width: 100%;">
                [Hình ảnh bí kíp minh họa đặt ở đây]
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="phuc" style="padding: 0; padding-bottom: 80px;">
        <div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 70vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; color: white; overflow: hidden;">
            <img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1v3_J21ZTGYeNVYXqcKZKruKDnnuAbGKj&sz=w1920"
                 alt="Phúc Background"
